# low

**Type Property**

The lowest-priority for a toolbar item.

## Declaration

```swift
static let low: NSToolbarItem.VisibilityPriority
```

## Discussion

The toolbar pushes items with this priority to the overflow menu first, even before items with the [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSToolbarItem/VisibilityPriority-swift.struct/standard] priority.

## Visibility priorities

- **standard**: The default visibility priority.
- **high**: A high priority that makes it less likely for the toolbar item to move to the overflow item.
- **user**: The highest priority for items in the toolbar.
